{
  "texts": [
    "For all tested outlet diameters, the optimal angle for minimizing the pressure loss is between 50°a nd 56°, and the relative improvement is around 5% to 5.5%.",
    "1 and parameters are in Table 1.",
    "Source: Authors own work",
    "In order to investigate if more complex geometries might yield further improvement, we now present the results from the spline parametrization.",
    "We ran the shape optimization using the same feeding rates and outlet diameters as in the angle optimization."
